@startuml
title Adapter - Estrutura

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class Client

interface Target {
  + request(): void
}

class Adapter {
  - adaptee: Adaptee
  + request(): void
}

class Adaptee {
  + specificRequest(): void
}

Client --> Target : usa
Adapter ..|> Target
Adapter --> Adaptee : traduz chamada

note right of Adapter
  Converte a interface esperada pelo cliente
  para a interface disponível no adaptee.
end note

@enduml

@startuml
title Adapter - Comunicação

actor Client
participant Adapter
participant Adaptee

Client -> Adapter : request()
Adapter -> Adapter : converte parâmetros e estrutura
Adapter -> Adaptee : specificRequest()
Adaptee --> Adapter : resposta original
Adapter -> Adapter : adapta resposta
Adapter --> Client : resposta no formato esperado

@enduml
